name: GOOFY
description: GOOFY DOGE is a mascot token based on the Solana chain, which pays tribute to the original World Cup mascot and provides an opportunity for those who missed the initial craze to experience its excitement. In the serious yet boundless realm of cryptocurrencies, GOOFY Meme Coin emerges to bring fresh air and endless laughter to the market. Inspired by the classic Disney character Goofy, this joyful and carefree friend, GOOFY Meme Coin is not just a digital currency but a cultural symbol representing an optimistic attitude towards life and a curious exploration of the unknown. Created by a group of Disney enthusiasts and blockchain technologists, the project aims to create a cryptocurrency ecosystem that is both entertaining and useful.
